'''梅斯纳尔山峰博物馆'''（Messner Mountain Museum，MMM）是意大利登山家[[莱茵霍尔德·梅斯纳尔|莱茵霍尔德·梅斯纳尔]]创建的[[博物馆|博物馆]]项目，位于意大利北部[[南蒂罗尔|南蒂罗尔]]地区。梅斯纳尔的博物馆项目旨在教育游客“人与山相遇”，涉及山脉和冰川的科学，登山和攀岩的历史，圣山的历史，以及山区居民的历史。<ref name="inhabit">{{cite web |last=Zimmer |first=Lori |title=Medieval Italian Castle Transformed into Modern Mountain Museum |work=Inhabit |url=http://inhabitat.com/medieval-italian-castle-transformed-into-modern-mountain-museum/ |accessdate=February 9, 2014 |archive-date=2017-09-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170926143603/http://inhabitat.com/medieval-italian-castle-transformed-into-modern-mountain-museum/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

该博物馆包括设在六个不同地点：

# MMM 菲尔米安，在[[博尔扎诺|博尔扎诺]]附近的[[西格蒙德城堡|西格蒙德城堡]]，是博物馆的核心，集中于人与山的关系。内容包括山区地质、在人类生活中山区的宗教意义、登山和高山旅游的历史<ref name="mmm-firmian">{{cite web |title=MMM Firmian |work=Messner Mountain Museum |url=http://www.messner-mountain-museum.it/en/firmian/museum/ |accessdate=October 21, 2016 |archive-date=2016-11-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161108171517/http://www.messner-mountain-museum.it/en/firmian/museum/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。
# MMM Juval，在Naturns附近中世纪的Juval城堡，关注世界各地的圣山（如[[冈仁波齐峰|冈仁波齐峰]]、[[富士山|富士山]]）及其宗教意义。<ref name="mmm-juval">{{cite web |title=MMM Juval |work=Messner Mountain Museum |url=http://www.messner-mountain-museum.it/en/juval/museum/ |accessdate=October 21, 2016 |archive-date=2016-11-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161128064432/http://www.messner-mountain-museum.it/en/juval/museum/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>于1995年开放<ref name="mmm-juval"/>。这座城堡由梅斯纳尔私人拥有，作为他的夏季住所。馆内有西藏佛教展品，包括一个巨大的[[转经轮|转经轮]]。
# MMM 多洛米蒂，在[[科尔蒂纳丹佩佐|科尔蒂纳丹佩佐]]和[[皮耶韦迪卡多雷|皮耶韦迪卡多雷]]之间高2181米的Rite山上，设于[[第一次世界大战|第一次世界大战]]堡垒中，成立于2002年，主题是岩石<ref name="mmm-dolomites">{{cite web |title=MMM Dolomites |work=Messner Mountain Museum |url=http://www.messner-mountain-museum.it/en/dolomites/museum/ |accessdate=October 21, 2016 |archive-date=2016-11-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161128064427/http://www.messner-mountain-museum.it/en/dolomites/museum/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>
# MMM Ortles，位于索尔达，2004年开放，关注登山和冰川的历史 <ref name="mmm-ortles">{{cite web |title=MMM Ortles |work=Messner Mountain Museum |url=http://www.messner-mountain-museum.it/en/ortles/museum/ |accessdate=October 21, 2016 |archive-date=2016-11-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161107192710/http://www.messner-mountain-museum.it/en/ortles/museum/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>
#MMM Ripa 在[[布鲁尼科|布鲁尼科]]城堡，关注亚洲，非洲，南美洲和欧洲的山地民族<ref name="mmm-ripa">{{cite web |title=MMM Ripa |work=Messner Mountain Museum |url=http://www.messner-mountain-museum.it/en/ripa/museum/ |accessdate=October 21, 2016 |archive-date=2016-11-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161108050114/http://www.messner-mountain-museum.it/en/ripa/museum/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>
# MMM Corones ，在科隆普拉茨山山顶（2,275米），开放于2015年7月，关注传统攀登<ref>{{cite web|title=MMM Corones|url=http://www.messner-mountain-museum.it/en/corones/museum/|website=Messner Mountain Museum|accessdate=21 October 2016|archive-date=2016-10-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161031102253/http://www.messner-mountain-museum.it/en/corones/museum/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。博物馆是一座现代建筑，由英国著名建筑师[[扎哈·哈迪德|扎哈·哈迪德]]设计<ref>{{cite web|title=Zaha Hadid's MMM Corones museum gazes at the mountains|url=https://www.inexhibit.com/case-studies/corones-museum-zaha-hadid-gazing-mountains|author=Federica Lusiardi|publisher=Inexhibit|accessdate=July 24, 2015|archive-date=2016-06-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160609140213/http://www.inexhibit.com/case-studies/corones-museum-zaha-hadid-gazing-mountains/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

